Name: Test of the USB3 IP Core from Daisho on a Xilinx device
Short Name: daisho
URL: https://github.com/enjoy-digital/daisho
License: BSD-2-Clause

Description:
This package is used as a testbench for the fpga-tool-perf project, to test performance and quality of results of different vendor and open source toolchains.

Local Modifications:
Use OBUFT instead of conditional assign to avoid inferring to _TBUF_.
Removal of unused variables.
Changed extension of .vh files to .v.
